high_descs: Move to stand in front of the small black table between the counter and trash bin.
Pick up the butter knife that's positioned horizontally from the black table.
Use the butter knife to slice the head of lettuce.
Carry the butter knife to long white table with the toaster on top.
Place the butter knife on the table, right of the toaster.
Move back to the black table with the lettuce.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the table.
Carry the slice of the lettuce to the stove.
Place the slice of lettuce in the pan on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the lettuce in it from the stove.
Carry the pan with the lettuce to the white table where you left the butter knife.
Place the pan with lettuce on the table and the back right corner.
anns.task_desc: Move a pan with a slice of lettuce to a white table.

high_descs: Walk to the small black table to the right of the black trash bag.
Pick up the knife in front of the lettuce on the black table.
Cut up the lettuce on the black table.
Turn left and walk to the white table.
Place the knife on the white table.
Turn right and walk to the lettuce on the black table.
Pick up a piece of lettuce on the black table.
Turn around and walk to the stove in the corner.
Place the piece of lettuce in the pot closest to you on the stove.
Pick up the pot closest to you on the stove.
Turn right and walk to the white table to the left of the black trash bag.
Place the pot on the upper right corner of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pot with a piece of lettuce in it on the white table next to the trash bag.

high_descs: go forward to end of counter to black table on the right with green melon
pick up knife in front of green melon
slice melon on black table
turn left, face table with toaster
place knife on table to the right of the toaster
turn left, face black table with green melon
pick up slice of green melon from black table
turn around, go to stove on the right
place green melon slice in square pan on front burner of stove
pick up square pan with melon slice
turn right, go to table with toaster, face knife on white table
place pan on back, right corner of white table
anns.task_desc: Place green melon slice in pan, place pan on back, right corner of table
